$interpreted: Dagger: Damn it! The tracks disappear. Where have they taken Angelia...?
Dagger: ...Eh, that is?
Uzziah: A glimmer wolf....the tribe lives on, so it seems?
Koll: ...Grrrrrooowuuu...
Dagger: HEY!
Dagger: HEY, YOU! Shady Slim, did you kidnap Angelia?
Koll: ……?
Uzziah: ……
Dagger: Silence is acceptance. Tell me where she is!
Uzziah: ...I don't understand what you mean. Please do not block my path.
Koll: Hoouuu?!
Dagger: Hey, where you going?
Dagger: What the... are you protecting me?
Dagger: You filthy flaming dreadful dog, don't you underestimate me!
Dagger: See what I'm capable of? I need no protection!
Koll: Woooerrrr………
Dagger: How does he summon monsters from nowhere? Feels like he didn't want to take our lives...
Dagger: Big dog, what you think?
Dagger: Hold on, he's gone! How are we supposed to follow him now?! I'm already at Paradise Prairie......
Koll: Woooerrrr?!
Dagger: Big dog, why are you looking over there with such sad eyes? Someone you know?
Dagger: Or was that once your home?
Koll: Woooerrr......
Dagger: Big dog, you have a keen nose, right?
Koll: Woooerrrr?!
Dagger: I'm looking for female human, who must have been taken from the rune chariot ahead.
Dagger: But I got lost on the prairie...
Koll: Wooo?
Dagger: If you use your sense of smell to help me find her, I'll accompany you on the prairie.

Dagger: Your snubbing will also be forgotten,
how's that for a deal?
Koll: Wooo...
Dagger: Picked up the scent that fast? Hey, wait for me!
Dagger: Found it again! Big dog, you sure got a sensitive nose... eh?
Dagger: Big dog, why won't you come over here? Thinking of something from the past?
Koll: ………
Dagger: ...Perhaps the reason is unspeakable...
Dagger: If so, what's your name? If I meet someone you know, I'll pass on a message.
Koll: Arrrooo~
Dagger: Right. I can't understand a thing. Not to mention how vast this prairie is;
Dagger: Fat chance I'd actually meet someone he knows...
Dagger: Alright, keep following these tracks and I'll catch the lot of you. Just wait and see!
